com.jamonapi.proxy
Class MonProxyFactory

java.lang.Object
  com.jamonapi.proxy.MonProxyFactory

public class MonProxyFactory
extends java.lang.Object

This static MonProxyFactory simply uses an instance of MonProxyFactoryImp to do its work. MonProxyFactoryImp can also be created in its own right directly. See its java docs for further info.

Mainly kept this class for backwards compatibility reasons.
